Musical data notice
==================

data/wurfelspiel.json was extracted from the
DiceWaltz-1.2.1WithContredanse package. The package metadata records this
upstream download location:

http://r.newman.ch/rpi/sounding-off/dwcontredanse.zip

The data consists of historical musical-dice-game selection tables and
LilyPond measure transcriptions. It is not covered by this repository's MIT
license. No license was present in the extracted package metadata, so users
must determine whether their intended use of the transcriptions is permitted.
